---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Meish Experience Audit — Meish"
  description="On-site observation of the human state across your guest journey: ranked friction points and a concrete improvement plan. Not mystery shopping."
>
  <section class="section container">
    <p class="eyebrow">Hotels · On-site</p>
    <h1>We measure what your guests feel — and hand you the fixes.</h1>
    <p class="lead">An on-site observation of the human state across your guest journey: where
      load builds, where presence breaks, where a small warmth moment is missing. You get a
      ranked list of friction points and a concrete plan — not a binder nobody reads.</p>

    <h2>What we look at</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Emotional guest journey — arrival → stay → departure → afterglow</li>
      <li>Sensory regulation — light, sound, scent, temperature, spatial rhythm</li>
      <li>Micro-attachments — the small moments of warmth that make a stay memorable</li>
      <li>Felt safety and recovery — did load actually decrease?</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What you get</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Ranked friction points, with the fix for each</li>
      <li>A Meish Experience Score (Hotel Audit and above)</li>
      <li>A 30-day improvement plan your team can act on</li>
      <li>A leadership debrief</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Choose your depth</h2>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Service</th><th>For whom</th><th>Outcome</th><th>From</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td><strong>Signal Audit</strong></td><td>Boutique, design, wellness, Lapland, experience-led hotels</td><td>10 friction points + 10 fixes + 60-min debrief</td><td>€3,500</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Hotel Audit</strong></td><td>Leadership ready for full-journey investment</td><td>Scored journey map + Meish Experience Score + 30-day plan</td><td>€7,500</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Transformation Sprint</strong></td><td>Premium properties post-repositioning</td><td>Room rituals + 30–90 day co-implementation</td><td>€25,000</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p><small>Prices exclude VAT; confirmed per property. Always “Meish Experience Signal
      Audit” — never bare “Signal Audit.”</small></p>

    <h2>Not mystery shopping</h2>
    <p>We don't grade your staff and we don't pose as secret critics. We observe the
      experience, with your knowledge, and protect everyone's dignity — see
      <a href="/privacy">boundaries</a>.</p>

    <p><a class="button button--primary" href="/contact">Book a Signal Audit</a></p>
  </section>
</Base>
